                                        fill="currentColor"></path>
                                    </svg>
                            </button>

                            <hr>

                            <h5 class="card-title fs-3">Changing Zip Code</h5>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Users can change their zip code by entering their new one in the “New Zip Code” field under the “Change Zip Code” section and clicking "Change Zip Code" button.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5 fw-bold">This is what the "Change Zip Code" section looks like:</p>

                            <img class="border mb-2" src="/static/other_images/changezip.png" alt="The Change Zip Code section of the account page" width="500px">

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Zip Codes are at minimum 5 characters and can only be numbers.</p>

                            <hr>

                            <h5 class="card-title fs-3">Logging Out</h5>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Users can also log out of their account by clicking the yellow “Logout” button in the “Logout” section.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5 fw-bold">This is what the logout button looks like:</p>
                            <button class="btn mb-2 tertiaryColor">Logout</button>

                            <hr>

                            <h5 class="card-title fs-3">Deleting Account</h5>
                            <p class="card-text fs-5">Users can delete their account by pressing the “Delete Account” button underneath the section of the same name.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5">When you click the "Delete Account" button, a pop up will appear to make sure you are sure about deleting your account. If you are sure about deleting your account, click the "Delete Account" button.</p>

                            <p class="card-text fs-5 fw-bold">This is what the "Delete Account" buttons look like:</p>

                            <button type="button" class="mt-2 btn btn-lg btn-danger">Delete Account</button>

                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
